headline: Goodles Thinks Mac and Cheese Shouldn’t Be Adults’ Secret Meal Anymore
summary: A new brand of macaroni and cheese is winning market share and taking over shelves with its colorful boxes, cheeky names and focus on young adults who previously may have seen packaged powder and noodles as a meal choice to hide.

headline: Catalina Snacks® Enters Granola Category with Bold New Protein-Packed Line
summary: Catalina Snacks®, a leading innovator redefining better-for-you snacks and cereals, is breaking into the granola aisle with the debut of Catalina Crunch® Protein Granola. This deliciously crunchy, lower-sugar granola is made to satisfy everyday cravings—whether you're fueling up for breakfast or need a snack on-the-go.
